                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I am with Bellanfear.. Unfortunately, most books based on worlds are written by people that have only read the box and then decided they wanted to write some books about it.
<br />
The big exception to that was the Dark Sun series from TSR (when it was still really TSR). That was a damn fine series based in the world. I enjoyed all of them.
<br />
