                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I heard its about a dark elf paladin named Ace Newtron, who does a bunch of farming of pelts and silks for the first half of the book, then gets frustrated by the lack of interest from the local merchants in his home town of Felwithe, so he goes to the barbarian village of Kaladim to seek his fortune.  Before he gets there though, he sells out his entire stock of qeynos midmorning teas which he foollishly spends on summoned bread and water just before camping for the night. The next day he begins his career as a slave mule working for the Yantis Corporation.
<br />

<br />
The sequel is about the inner torment he faces when he is hired as a a desk cleric in the Freeport Bank.  Apparently he went stark raving mad at the isolation of it all, but there was no one there to hear him so its sorta a happy ending.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
