        <tr>
		<td width="150" align="left" valign="top" class="row1"><a name="86307"></a><span class="name"><span class="usercolor">Yakk</span></span></td>
                <td class="row1" width="100%" height="28" valign="top"><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
                        <tr>
                                <td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td><a href="viewtopic.php?p=86307#86307"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Nov 17, 2004 6:18 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: </span></td>
                                <td align="right" valign="top" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=86307"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>    </td></tr></table></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><hr /></td>
                        </tr>
                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody"></span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Vahen wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Salvatore may have created a "world within a world" But he still gave us no real reason on why his main character turned out chaotic good in a chaotic evil enviroment with NO role model. Also for a race that has 1 child every 50 odd years, they are very free with the nightly rituals of killing off the dark elven males.... in a town of less then 20,000 dark elves :p. Little thing like that make me detest Salvatore and his writing style.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
<br />

<br />
Ob Geek:
<br />

<br />
Say they have 15000 females and 5000 males.
<br />

<br />
The 15000 females, at one child/50 years, generate 300 children a year.  Half of them are male.
<br />

<br />
That's 150 males.  Now, assuming otherwise simular male/female death rates, to keep a 3 female:1 male ratio, they are required to kill an average of 100 males/year.
<br />

<br />
How long do elves have to live, before old age death, to maintain a steady population?
<br />

<br />
Americans have an accidental death rate of 0.04% or so (40 per 100,000), and homicide+suicide rates that almost match this.  Elves might be more careful, but they are in a much more dangerous world.
<br />

<br />
Let say the elvish non-age related death rate is 0.1%/annum.  This means 39% of elves die before they reach 500, or 63% by the time they hit 1000.  Violent/accidental death would be a leading cause of death to elves (for humanity, voilent/accidental death is small enough that it almost disappears in the statistical noise of cancer/cardeo-vascular deaths).
<br />

<br />
So, 1% of the females in the city have a female child every year, and 0.1% per year die from accidents/suicide.
<br />

<br />
This means 0.9% have to die of old age.
<br />

<br />
111 year lifespan.  This doesn't work.
<br />

<br />
Ok, lets make dark elven life brutal.  They need a 1000 year natural lifespan, so 0.1% on average die per year from old age.  Which puts their accident rate at 0.9%.
<br />

<br />
Which means only 40% of the elves live to 100.  16% to 200.  2.6% to 400.  0.07% to 800.
<br />

<br />
These elves are too fertile for their lifespan.
<br />

<br />
Lets make dark elves give birth to 3 males for every 1 female, and half their birth rate: 1 child per century.
<br />

<br />
Now, a female has 1 female child every 400 years on average, and one male child every 133 years.
<br />

<br />
Lets also have a population of 16000 female to 4000 male.  So that's 120 male births per year and 40 female births.
<br />

<br />
To maintain the 4 female:1 male ratio, they have to kill an extra 110 males/year.  Or about 2 per week.  Munchy crunchy.
<br />

<br />
0.25% female birth rate by population.  This has to match the death rate of females, and results in a 400 year average lifespan.
<br />

<br />
A 1000 year old-age means about 0.1% of the population dies of old age every year, leaving a 0.15% rate for other causes.  Or about 24 females/year.
<br />

<br />
This generates a socieity that is about twice as risky, accident/violence wise, than modern USA for females, a 400 year average lifespan, and a 277 median lifespawn (half of the females die before the age of about 277).  This is a bit off - the accidential/violent death rate could vary by age  like it does in the human population.
<br />

<br />
So there is some reasonable demographic statisticis.
<br />

<br />
1&gt; 3 male live births for every female live birth.
<br />
2&gt; 1 live birth for every 100 females on average.  Possibly higher during fertile years, and less at old age.
<br />
3&gt; 16000 females, 4000 males
<br />
4&gt; 16 deaths by old age amoung the women/year.
<br />
5&gt; 24 deaths by accident/violence amoung the women/year.
<br />
6&gt; 4 deaths by old age amoung the men/year
<br />
7&gt; 116 deaths by accident/violence amoung the men/year, or a bit over 2 / week.
<br />
8&gt; 60% of females die by violence/accident.  97% of men die by accident/violence.
<br />
9&gt; Average female death age is 400.  Median as low as 277.
<br />
10&gt; Average male death age could be as low as 33.  Median as low as 23.
<br />

<br />
As a note, I know little about RAS's drow.  Was just feeling number crunchy.</span><span class="postbody"></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
                        </tr>
                </table></td>
